The changes weren't implemented properly on the PBE. [It currently heals for 35-50% less than expected.
](http://boards.pbe.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bugs/GnmEYA9i-sona-aria-of-perseverence-healing-for-35-50-less-than-the-intended-amount)
Would it be possible to take a look before changes get locked? I'd hate to play 2-3 with a bugged heal.

> Rammus - Reducing early ganking/dueling power a bit basically. This one especially we'll want to monitor closely, keep an eye on how Rammus does once the new jungle changes roll out.


Haha.  Roll out. {{champion:33}} 


Puns aside, how has rammus been doing in the pbe jungle?  I've heard the early clear is really difficult for most champions, especially the new wraith camp.  Will this be so limiting that champions like rammus completely lose jungle viability due to insufficient clear speeds?
